<br>
if however your a more casual player that enjoys a slower leveling curve and raiding is not much your cup of tea then look at some of the smaller social guilds on the server that are more intent on a friendly game environment more so than killing uber mob_1.  If thats your desire I would suggest a guild like Raving lunatics great group of folks many lower level toons but there a social bunch mostly not really power gamers.<br>
<br>
